---
title: Crispy Sunchoke Salad with Kale, Mushrooms & Farro
description: If you've never tried sunchokes, hold onto your hat. Crispy, nutty sunchokes are this salad's pièce de résistance. Creamy goat cheese and crunchy pepitas complete the texture spectrum in this hearty kale and farro salad.
